有台仔幫加上自己偷技術已經進步好大架喇。<br />\n好似塑膠合成加工已經攞晒台灣技術踢走人地添喇。以前大陸連似樣少少既膠粒都做唔出，D車既內飾件都要買人地既膠粒材料，而家全部大陸做。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"同樣系化工技術：<br />\n中國做到塑㬵合成加工<br />\n人地已經做緊納米<br />\n<br />\n同樣系半導體技術：<br />\n中國只能做 封裝測試（下游）<br />\n人地做緊 IC設計/晶圓代工（上游）"},{"pid":"6609bd3f58783ea2a216a8e5e5787338e5bf3782","tid":992290,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0bc9678099bada3058d94762f6073b32a93676c","tid":992290,"uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"落後10年，即係有10年進步空間，又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"咁11年後就可以屌打美帝了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428509bc3f86e71d548b177e1a54433945555332","tid":992290,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"十年可能只係相差一至兩代 , 外媒小罵大幫忙 , 暗中抬高支那"},{"pid":"3df0b8f4bfa3e8985ea4b782b5f6428ebbe92aa2","tid":992290,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21171cbc3b43a244090bd8d64c9ad0d3346e5e81","tid":992290,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f7a2bc529ae25d6029459b2a91dea4d0a21e9ce","tid":992290,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"支那仲要無光刻機量產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"偷台灣好快有"},{"pid":"af20f87957c5308a67cd8a6d2aa3c175b79b8e39","tid":992290,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"做唔做到2008既野？？"},{"pid":"5e1bb4fbc344c650c4d394b009110cfc0885e197","tid":992290,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"何止10年"},{"pid":"d23d9516654400fe28820419467af99f3fabfeca","tid":992290,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:19